snippet.title: Pre-Calculus - Evaluate the difference quotient
snippet.description: This video explains how to evaluate the difference quotient, and simplify it.  Remember to put parentheses around the function that is being subtracted, so you do not lose any negative signs.  For more videos please visit http://www.mysecretmathtutor.com
